      • getBlockedAmounts

        @GET
 @Path(value="/users/me/wallet/blocked-amounts")
List<BlockedAmount> getBlockedAmounts(@HeaderParam(value="X-Size")
                                                                                            int pageSize,
                                                                                            @HeaderParam(value="X-Page")
                                                                                            int pageNo)
        Retrieve blocked amounts in the wallet, that either represent a pending investment, or investor's fee. This query is paginated.
        Parameters:
        pageSize - How many items should be listed on the page.
        pageNo - Number of the page to show, where 0 is the first page.
        Returns:
        Blocked amount on that particular page.
